hopobject.body: Excellent work, Nice Design seahealthstore.com "To be able to sit alongside Mariano in that bullpen in his final All-Star Game appearance would be an awfully special moment in my career," said Robertson, who was selected in 2012. "Yankees fans are the best, and I know that they will make every effort to send me to Queens." For Harvey making the team was a goal and he would like to be chosen to start it by Bochy, who will skipper the National League team. His next start, Monday, coincidentally will be against Bochy's Giants.
